{"id":"1391e9a9-7257-434c-80ba-0cb6356e8e2a","name":"Taunie, Leader of Team MZ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Within the grand Lumiose City resides Hotel Z. Ran by AZ, this shabby establishment is the home base of Team MZ, a group of young misfits that work together to keep the city safe. Led by Taunie, Team MZ faces the issue of Rogue Mega Pokémon appearing all over Lumiose, threatening the peace for all that live in it.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(208, 148, 148);\"><strong><em>Pokémon</em></strong></span><strong><em> </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 163, 163);\"><strong><em>Legends:</em></strong></span><strong><em> </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 208, 136);\"><strong><em>Z-A.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 188, 114);\">Art by </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/R3dFiVe_artist/status/1978920678121263327\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 188, 114);\"><strong><em>R3dFiVe</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 188, 114);\"><strong><em>.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x58P-Wljw4jQyhBIpGLOJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><em>First bot I've made to have multiple intros (if they save, anyways... they've been giving me trouble)! They're both quite similar and follow how you actually meet Taunie in Z-A, with the second one following the events of that meeting a bit closer due to a certain Pancham. I'll likely add more as time goes on.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 183, 183);\">(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3yvsT5C3BbhwM9Nppeyh4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3d6276c0-0cd3-40f1-a8c5-15697598b353_character-emma-of-the-looker-bureau\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Emma</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- Head detective of Lumiose City's Looker Bureau from Pokémon Legends Z-A.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dc1f9b63-616c-4a16-97fe-f89f6ccfb1d1_character-akari-survey-corps-aide\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Akari</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- The female protagonist and member of the Survey Corps of Pokémon Legends: Arceus.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/15ae45db-d828-4348-9589-2759a66d8180_character-alpha-gardevoir\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Alpha Gardevoir</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- The dangerous alpha Pokémon of Alabaster Icelands from Pokémon Legends: Arceus.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"qO6JNBnXknFZy-UBoKx3H.webp","creator":"HouseOrdelia","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🐙 Pokemon","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":2355,"messages":53668,"created_at":"2025-10-20T12:14:57.247160+00:00"}